rows.label: qst003206_msg0001
rows.name:
Bonono-kun!? Bonono-kun!! I'm
so glad, so glad you're okay!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, I managed to survive somehow,
mo. If help had been any later, it
would have been dangerous, mo.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0003
rows.name: Whew, that was quite a thrill, mo.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0004
rows.name:
That distance I fell, whoooosh...
Isn't that a record for a Nopon, mo?

rows.label: qst003206_msg0005
rows.name:
You can't get a thrill like that
anywhere else, mo! I'm starting
to want to do it again, mo!!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0006
rows.name: ...Don't.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0007
rows.name: Alulu never wants to fall again, mo...

rows.label: qst003206_msg0008
rows.name: ...And who is this?

rows.label: qst003206_msg0009
rows.name:
This is Alulu-chan, mo.
She fell from Acedia onto
the World Tree with me.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0010
rows.name:
When we fell on the World Tree,
I landed on Bonono-kun and he
cushioned my fall, mo.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0011
rows.name:
Whoa, a rare story of you
being cool, Bonono-kun?

rows.label: qst003206_msg0012
rows.name: It's not rare, mo!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0013
rows.name:
After that, when we were attacked
by enemies, he left me behind and
ran away at full speed, mo...

rows.label: qst003206_msg0014
rows.name: Gulp...

rows.label: qst003206_msg0015
rows.name:
What's more, Alulu even teamed
up with a Blade-san and
defeated three enemies, mo.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0016
rows.name:
Wow... Alulu-chan, you're
way cooler than him!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0017
rows.name: Oh, you're making me blush, mo!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0018
rows.name:
W-well, what matters is that
everyone is safe, mo! All's
well that ends well, mo!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0019
rows.name: You're right. We have to thank them.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0020
rows.name: Thank you all so very much, mo!
